data.description: Very nice, updated Ranch home in Osage. Single Attached Garage and Oversized Double Detached garage in Back of Home. Fenced in Backyard. Lower Level has some partial finish with a Bedroom with Egress. Newer Kitchen and Flooring. Great location.  Move quickly and Call your REALTOR today!! This property will be gone fast!!
